%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5e28c2e20bb6c4240a55d8edffb777ec, type: 3}
  m_Name: AstralHouseIntro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NewDialogueData
  npcName: Chime
  dialogueLines:
  - LineID: Start
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Oh! You finally woke up.
    lineTone: 1
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: 
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices:
    - text: Why does everything look...different?
      NextLineID: Part II
      moralityChange: 1
      direction: 0
      objectiveToActivate: 
    - text: Who the **** are you?!
      NextLineID: 
      moralityChange: -1
      direction: 0
      objectiveToActivate: 
    - text: This is what I get for eating random berries in the forest.
      NextLineID: Part II
      moralityChange: 1
      direction: 2
      objectiveToActivate: 
    - text: Can you get away from me? Like, right now?
      NextLineID: Part II
      moralityChange: -1
      direction: 3
      objectiveToActivate: 
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: Part II
    Speaker: Chime
    text: I'm sure you have many questions, I'll do my best to explain. My name is
      Chime, your guiding fairy, and we're in the astral plane now. This is the astral
      form of your house.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: 
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices:
    - text: What is the 'astral plane?
      NextLineID: Part III
      moralityChange: 1
      direction: 0
      objectiveToActivate: 
    - text: Respectfully, where the **** am I exactly?
      NextLineID: 
      moralityChange: 1
      direction: 2
      objectiveToActivate: 
    - text: Yeah, that doesn't make things any clearer.
      NextLineID: Part III
      moralityChange: -1
      direction: 1
      objectiveToActivate: 
    - text: Should I even bother? Can I go back to sleep?
      NextLineID: Part III
      moralityChange: -1
      direction: 3
      objectiveToActivate: 
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: Part III
    Speaker: Chime
    text: The astral plane is set in the past, but it's your present. You're special,
      Echo. Your involvement with everyone here saw to your awakening of powers.
      I'm here to guide you, so you can use those powers to better everyone's outcomes.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: Part VI
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: Part VI
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Earlier today, your friends spoke of the people they lost, and how they
      wish they could have changed the past. Here, you can do just that, as a mediator
      of sorts.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: Part V
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: Part V
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Can you help your friends move forward, without regret?
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: Part V
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices:
    - text: Yes, I can!
      NextLineID: Good
      moralityChange: 1
      direction: 0
      objectiveToActivate: 
    - text: I'm not sure, but I'll try.
      NextLineID: Good
      moralityChange: 1
      direction: 2
      objectiveToActivate: 
    - text: Why should I? I've got my own problems.
      NextLineID: Bad
      moralityChange: -1
      direction: 1
      objectiveToActivate: 
    - text: You know, you're asking a lot of someone who just woke up.
      NextLineID: Bad
      moralityChange: -1
      direction: 3
      objectiveToActivate: 
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: Good
    Speaker: Chime
    text: That's the spirit! Let's get going.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: Part VI
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: Bad
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Helping the others will fix your biggest problem. Just trust me.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: Part VI
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: Part VI
    Speaker: Chime
    text: I saw you grab a map before you went to bed last night, do you still have
      it?
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: End
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: End
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Looking at the map, it seems we'll have to go through a gate in The Graveyard.
      Grab what you need, and when you're ready, we'll head out.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: 
    NextLineID: 
    endDialogueAfterLine: 1
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
